Dialogs.Dialog: (Well, I have finished today's library committee duty... Eh？ Where is ▲小早川＊▲？)
(A message from ▲小早川＊▲...)
"I'm waiting for you on the rooftop. -Rinko."
(Rooftop...？ Don't tell me...)
Hah... Hah... ▲小早川＊▲！！
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
▲小早川＊▲... So you are here. Hah...
Again, you're making that face while gasping for breath...
Well...
I'm fine... I'm not crying.
Okay then...
It's just that the sunset is very beautiful, so I thought that you might want to see it too.
I'm not calling you out only when I'm sad. When I'm happy, I want to share the happy moment, too.
Okay... I see.
Hey, you're making that face again.
What kind of face？
That usual mature-looking face... It makes you look weird.
Don't say that I'm weird...
Hehe. Hey, do you remember the first time we met？
I remember. It was such a warm day.
Yeah... I hate spring.
There are new students and new classes... But none of them matters for me.
It makes me realize how lonely I am.
But from now on, when I think of spring, I will be reminded of the time we met instead.
That's good then...
It was such a hot day. The shade of that tree really felt so nice.
That is my favorite spot. I always go there to read a book when something bothers me.
Reading a book alone makes me feel as if I'm the only person existing in the world.
I see. So I disturbed you, huh？
You did. And since you were there, I wasn't the only one in my world anymore.
Ah, it was during fall's reading week.
Right. The library was very crowded, so I randomly picked a book and borrowed it to read outside.
That book turned out to be a romantic novel, the kind that I hated most.
That's why I was mean to you when you called out to me. It was somewhat like a scene from a cheesy drama...
I see. That was such a bad timing, huh？
Yeah, it was on a very cold day...
Yeah. Sorry... I was mean to you.
With the winter arranging of all the bookshelves, huh？
But... at that time, I thought that it would be all right for me to be alone.
Unlike now, I didn't have any ally back then...
Hey, did you stare at me at that time？
Well... Did I？
You did. I really saw it.
And... you're totally different from the person I had imagined. The person who exists in my world, who will love only me.
Totally different？
Yes.
Not even a little bit？
Not at all.
Didn't you at least think that I was handsome or something？
What should I say...？ I can't recall what I thought about that back then.
What I can always recall is this kind of facial expression.
...My expression？
Yeah, this gentle and a little troubled face. The face that I love most.
Hey... I love you this much. Too much that I don't know what to do...
Up until now, I thought that it would be okay if you think of me as your sister, but...
That is not good anymore. I want you to love me more than that, and...
I want you... to be my boyfriend.
I love you, too
I'm sorry
I also love you... I want you to be my girlfriend, ▲小早川＊▲.
Okay, I'll be your girlfriend... Thanks.
Hehe... This is a little awkward, right？
Sort of, yeah...
Ah, you're making that troubled face again.
Eh？ Really？
Really. Actually, you only think of Rinko as your sister, right？
That's not true.
Really？
Really.
Then come this way...
...Can I kiss you？
...Yeah. Since I'm your girlfriend...
This is totally different from what I imagined.
Really...？ Sorry then.
No. It's much more heart throbbing than what I've ever imagined...
Much more？
Yeah, now I feel like I love you even more...
I really love you.
Actually, I don't think of you that way...
For me, I only think of you as my little sister ▲小早川＊▲.
...I'm sorry.
No... I also thought that it could have turned out this way.
You're making that troubled face again.
I'm okay. See？ I'm not crying.
Yeah, that's right...
Hey, I have a question.
If I'm like your sister, you will always be my ally, right？
Yeah. Even if it's "Rinko and I VS. the world," I'll be on your side.
...Then let's make a pact.
Hehe... From now on, I'll probably cause you a lot of troubles.
(All right, this is all for today's work at the library... Eh？ Where is ▲小早川＊▲？)
(A message from ▲小早川＊▲...)
"What's up？ I'm on the rooftop. - Rinko"
What is she doing on the rooftop...？ Could it be that...)
Hah, hah... ▲小早川＊▲！！
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
▲小早川＊▲... So you are here. Hah...
So slow. What if I were crying, huh？
...Were you crying？
No... I promised that I wouldn't be crying alone anymore.
I see. That's right.
Hey, you're making that face like a worrying big brother again.
Am I making that kind of face？
You are. Although you said that I wasn't your little sister.
I know.
That's fine though...
Do you remember the first time we met？
I remember. It was such a warm day.
For me... I hate spring.
There are new students and new classes... But none of them matters for me.
I know it's because of my personality that I failed to make any friends...
That's why I was mean to people back then. Sorry.
Oh, it's okay now.
It was such a hot day. The shade of that tree really felt so nice.
Right. That was Rinko's special spot.
It's where I can enjoy reading a book without anyone disturbing. It's like the world where Rinko is the only one exists.
I see. So I disturbed you on that day.
Yeah... And since you were there, I wasn't the only one in my world anymore.
Ah, it was during fall's reading week.
Yeah. and because of that, the library was very crowded, so I randomly picked a book and borrowed it to read outside...
That book turned out to be a romantic novel, the kind that I hated most.
And you happened to call out to me. It was somewhat like a cheesy drama...
That was why you were in a bad mood？
Sorry...
Yeah, it was on a very cold day...
Yeah.
The winter arranging of all the bookshelves, huh？
You really remember... Are you still angry？
I'm not angry.
Hehe... That's good.
Hey, did you stare at me at that time？
...Did I？
You did. What were you thinking？
I was thinking that... you were so cute.
I see... Sorry.
For what？
I was thinking that you were a pervert... Just for a while though.
R-Really...？
Because... You didn't seem like someone who's older than me at all.
Not at all？
I sometimes imagine that there will be someone who will find me.
Someone, the only one in this world, who will love me.
But, it's weird. Whenever I try to picture that person...
I see this face.
This face...？
Yeah, the face that always seems worried about Rinko. The face that Rinko likes the most in this world.
I must be pretty dumb, right？ To not realize this sooner.
Ever since you said you'd be my ally...
I've fallen in love with you... ever since then. I even feel like crying.
That's why I don't want to be like your little sister.
That's not what I want. I want you to love me.
I want you to take me as your girlfriend.
I love you, too
I'm sorry
I also love you. I want you to be my girlfriend, ▲小早川＊▲...
...Really？
I don't want to be your little sister, you know？？
I know.
Then... How much do you love me？
How much...？ Very, very much.
That's not understandable...
Well then... How about you ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko loves you 10 times more than you love her.
That's not understandable either.
You'll understand. ...Come over here.
It's 10 times more, right？
I was so nervous and I still don't understand.
Me, neither... My heart was throbbing and I don't understand a thing...
Now then, let's do it once more...
No. It's Rinko's lips, so you can't do this as you please.
That's...
Hehe... I'm being mean to you again.
Just once more would be good, right...？
Actually, I don't think of you that way...
For me, I only think of you as my little sister, ▲小早川＊▲.
...I'm sorry.
I understand... I have already known that.
But, I just couldn't hold it in anymore...
I'm sorry, but I...
It's okay if I cry when I'm with you, right？
I'm not crying. Hehe...
Well, you will always be my ally, right？
Of course, even if it's going to be you "and I VS. the world", ▲小早川＊▲.
...Okay.
(Okay, I've finished my library committee duty for today... Eh？ Where's ▲小早川＊▲？)
(A message from ▲小早川＊▲...)
"The sunset is beautiful, you know？ - Rinko."
(Sunset？ Is she on the rooftop...？ Oh no...)
Hah, hah... ▲小早川＊▲！！
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
▲小早川＊▲... You're here, huh？ Hah...
Sorry, I made you worry again...
Oh well.
I'm fine... I'm not crying.
Okay, I see.
I just want to watch the sunset together with you. It's very beautiful.
Yeah... It really is.
Not just when I'm crying, I want to be with you when I'm happy, too.
That's good.
You're making that face that looks like a worrying onii-chan again.
Am I？
Yeah, you are. You look kind and somewhat troubled.
This is quite embarrassing.
Hehe. Hey, do you remember the first time we met？
I remember. It was such a warm day.
Yeah... But, you know, I hate spring.
There are new students and new classes... But none of them matters for me.
It even makes me feel... lonelier that way.
But, I'm fine now. When I think back about that day, I...
It was such a hot day. The shade of that tree really felt so nice.
That was the spot where I usually went to read a book when I felt sad.
Reading a book where there is nobody around would take me out of the sorrow.
I see... So I was bothering you then？
No... Actually, since that day, I...
Ah, it was during fall's reading week.
Right, it was quite rare that the library was quite crowded.
The book I borrowed on that day was a romantic novel that I hated...
But somehow I was quite into it once I started reading...
That's why I was startled when you called out to me.
It was like a scene from the novel and I felt so embarrassed.
I had never imagined that things would turn out to be like this now...
It was a cold day... And you asked me to do the winter arranging of all the bookshelves, right？
Sorry... I was so mean to you, right？
It's okay now.
At that time, I really enjoyed being alone by myself.
I had never imagined that I would have had this kind of feeling...
Hey, did you stare at me at that time？
Well... Did I？
I saw it... I was also looking at you. That's why I know.
Really...？ I see...
When we first met, you were totally different from the person I had imagined...
What do you mean？
Although I prefer to be alone in my world, I'm longing for someone to love me for who I am.
And that person must be very handsome.
Hey, with that face, you're thinking that Rinko is so mean, right？？
At that time, you also made this kind of face.
It looks like you are searching for something deep inside Rinko's heart.
If you're like this, you'll be able to see who Rinko really is.
I don't really understand...
This troubled but gentle face...
It's the face that I love most in the world. Whenever I see this face, I even feel like crying...
Earlier, I thought it'd be okay that you thought of me as your little sister...
But, now... I don't want it like that.
I want you to love me more and more.
Not as your little sister, but as your girlfriend.
I love you... I really love you.
I love you, too
I'm sorry
I also love you. I want you to be my girlfriend ▲小早川＊▲....
Say that again... Say that you love me again.
Okay... I love you ▲小早川＊▲.
Hehe...
▲名前▲... Rinko loves you... Rinko really loves you.
It's strange. Every time I say the word "love," I feel the pain in my chest.
That's true...
Shall I try it once more？ I've been longing to know.
Ah, fine.
Hehe... As I thought.
I felt more pain in my chest than when I said the word "love."
A kiss is something we do when just the word "love" is not enough, right？
Um, I think so.
We should have tried this earlier, huh？
We can always do this any time we want.
Not any time. Only when we "love" each other much much more.
I see...
Hey, you're making that troubled face again-- ...Ah.
Now, we really love each other much more, right...？
Actually, I don't think of you that way...
For me, you'll always like my little sister, ▲小早川＊▲.
...I'm sorry.
Hey... You're making that troubled face again.
...Yeah.
That's right... It's better this way.
For me, I like that face that looks like a worrying onii-chan the most.
I have a question.
Will you always be Rinko's ally？
Of course I will. Even if -it's going to be "Rinko and I VS. the world."
Thanks... Hehe. I'll bear with it then. For now...
Please treat me nicely from now on, onii-chan▼
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
Umm, can I call you by your given name after this？
Sure, that's fine
It's fine as it is
Well then...
From now on, please take good care of me, ▲主人公＊▲.
Ah... Well, okay. I'll call you like this for a little while then.
Don't be so unclear... Well, I've decided to call you by your name now...
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.

Sure, that's fine

Hehe...

Don't be such a wishy- washy. I'll call you by your given name then.

Sure, that's fine

Confused？ I'll call you by your given name then. It's settled.

I'll think about it

Rinko
